`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
1. **Merging type-switch cases** (`case ReviewerEditorClosedMsg, BatchReviewerEditorClosedMsg`) is the right tool to keep cyclomatic complexity under the `gocyclo` limit of 30 — both cases share identical semantics (close the overlay), so no information is lost.
2. The **`▶` indicator** as a section-focus marker reuses `PopupSectionFocused` style without any new styles — the existing style set already has visual contrast between `PopupSection` (unfocused) and `PopupSectionFocused` (focused), making panel switching immediately obvious.
3. MRs without a JIRA key gracefully produce `Apply to (0 MRs) / (no sibling MRs)` — the nil-siblings path handles the `SiblingMRs("")` return value correctly since `ExtractJiraID` returns `""` for titles with no JIRA pattern.
